# Scope Boundary

Referenced from `AGENTS.md`.

## Rule

Work **only** inside `gumimap-v2/`. This is the project root.

- Do not read, reference, or modify files in parent directories (`../`, `../../`, etc.)
- Do not import patterns, scripts, configs, or code from sibling projects
- Do not search outside `gumimap-v2/` unless the user explicitly expands scope
- All git commands, scripts, and paths resolve from `gumimap-v2/`

## When in doubt

If a file path does not start with or live inside `gumimap-v2/`, do not use it.